y\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mao Ning, spokesperson for the ministry, said in the statement that Shen will also visit Serbia from August 12 to 14 at the invitation of the government of Serbia.\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mao_Ning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mao Ning\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mao_Ning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mao_Ning\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9477750001301452, \"rank\": 0.05479174057547437, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9477750001301452, \"rank\": 0.05479174057547437, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China attaches great importance to the development of sports and actively participates in the international Olympic Movement, Mao said.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 697, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999618610399323, \"rank\": 3.709987121333788e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mao_Zedong\", \"score\": 0.9999999982110239, \"rank\": 1.78891972696567e-09, \"text\": \"Mao\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mao_Zedong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mao_Zedong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During President Xi's visit to France in May this year, he expressed his support for France in hosting a successful Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9591254460897629, \"rank\": 0.04176261040963384, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9591254460897629, \"rank\": 0.04176261040963384, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999662347829918, \"rank\": 3.376635707586281e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vice President Han Zheng attended the opening ceremony, and State Councilor Shen Yiqin will attend the closing ceremony of the event, both as President Xi's special representatives.\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Han_Zheng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Han Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Han_Zheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Han_Zheng\"}, {\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Council_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 0.999999987613137, \"rank\": 1.238695419039201e-08, \"text\": \"State Councilor\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Council_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Council_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shen_Yiqin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shen Yiqin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shen_Yiqin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shen_Yiqin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This fully demonstrates how much China values and supports the international Olympic cause and the work of France as the Games host.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999618610399323, \"rank\": 3.709987121333788e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9591254460897629, \"rank\": 0.04176261040963384, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China applauds the success we have already seen in the hosting of the Paris 2024 Games and wishes it a full success in the coming days,\\\" said the spokesperson.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999618610399323, \"rank\": 3.709987121333788e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China and Serbia are ironclad friends, and the bilateral relations have maintained robust growth under the strategic guidance of the two heads of state, Mao said.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999618610399323, \"rank\": 3.709987121333788e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1462, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9477750001301452, \"rank\": 0.05479174057547437, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mao_Zedong\", \"score\": 0.9999999982110239, \"rank\": 1.78891972696567e-09, \"text\": \"Mao\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mao_Zedong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mao_Zedong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In May this year, President Xi paid a successful state visit to Serbia.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1680, \"end\": 1686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9477750001301452, \"rank\": 0.05479174057547437, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two heads of state jointly announced that the two sides will build a community with a shared future in the new era, opening up a new chapter for the history of bilateral relations, the spokesperson said.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During her upcoming visit, Shen will have in-depth communication with Serbian leaders on delivering on the important common understandings reached between the two heads of state, explore deeper practical cooperation and people-to-people and cultural exchanges between the two countries, and help bring China-Serbia relations to a new level.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.5365429801883135, \"rank\": 0.8362490591810919, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\\u2013Serbia_relations\", \"score\": 0.9999999999479314, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China-Serbia relations\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\\u2013Serbia_relations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\\u2013Serbia_relations\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(With input from Xinhua)  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2256, \"end\": 2262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.685437381833506e-26, \"text\": \"Xinhua\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\"}]}]}"